      <title>普京签署法律允许被告入伍并避免起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/putin-signs-law-allowing-accused-to-enlist-and-avoid-prosecution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统普京签署了一项法案，允许犯罪嫌疑人加入俄罗斯军队以避免受到起诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/putin-signs-law-allowing-accused-to-enlist-and-avoid-prosecution</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:19:13 GMT</pubDate>
