    <item>
      <title>中情局加大在中国招募人才力度，利用民众对习近平的不满</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/cia-boosts-china-recruiting-effort-to-exploit-discontent-with-xi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国中央情报局 (CIA) 正在加大力度招募中国公民，试图利用美国官员所说的对习近平主席统治日益增长的不满情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/cia-boosts-china-recruiting-effort-to-exploit-discontent-with-xi</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:15:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国保守党领袖竞争对手就税收和移民问题展开辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/rivals-pitch-leadership-plans-for-ousted-tories-key-takeaways</link>
      <description><![CDATA[四位接替里希·苏纳克成为英国保守党领袖的候选人将出席在伯明翰举行的保守党年度会议，向党员们介绍自己的竞选策略，党员们将在一个月后做出最终决定。在两位领跑者凯米·巴德诺赫和罗伯特·詹里克最近遭遇挫折后，保守党议员和官员告诉彭博社，竞选结果更加公开透明。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/rivals-pitch-leadership-plans-for-ousted-tories-key-takeaways</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 12:55:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朔尔茨再次呼吁尽快结束南方共同市场谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/scholz-makes-fresh-plea-for-speedy-conclusion-to-mercosur-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨再次呼吁迅速完成欧盟与南美四个经济体之间一项主要贸易协定的谈判，该协定遭到法国的反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/scholz-makes-fresh-plea-for-speedy-conclusion-to-mercosur-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 11:19:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国计划在 2025 年削减 600 亿欧元支出并提高税收</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/france-plans-66-billion-in-spending-cuts-and-tax-hikes-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 寻求收回不断扩大的预算赤字并增强投资者对法国的信心，该国计划明年削减约 600 亿欧元（664 亿美元）的支出并提高税收。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/france-plans-66-billion-in-spending-cuts-and-tax-hikes-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列誓言对伊朗大规模导弹袭击进行报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/israel-vows-retaliation-for-massive-iranian-missile-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗向以色列发射了约 200 枚弹道导弹后，本杰明内塔尼亚胡誓言要对伊朗进行报复，世界大国担心这一重大升级可能升级为中东战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/israel-vows-retaliation-for-massive-iranian-missile-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 07:06:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列大使馆附近发生爆炸后，丹麦警方拘留三名瑞典人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/denmark-boosts-security-near-israeli-embassy-as-blasts-probed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦警方拘留了与哥本哈根以色列大使馆附近两起爆炸案有关的三名瑞典国民，并正在调查该事件是否与斯德哥尔摩以色列外交使团附近发生的枪击事件有关。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/denmark-boosts-security-near-israeli-embassy-as-blasts-probed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 06:24:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃尔兹抓住选举主张，万斯语气软化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/walz-vance-spar-over-how-to-handle-iran-as-vp-debate-opens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周二的辩论中，副总统候选人在移民、堕胎和气候变化等问题上争论不休，共和党人 JD Vance 在很大程度上成功消除了他的强硬派声誉，而民主党人 Tim Walz 则表现出了紧张情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/walz-vance-spar-over-how-to-handle-iran-as-vp-debate-opens</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 01:13:38 GMT</pubDate>
